  "texts": [
    "• The government of the community/village committee conforms to and agrees with this study protocol; • No other intervention programs are being implemented in this community/village; • Distance of at least 2 km to other included villages to minimize contamination risk.",
    "Exclusion criteria• Less than 5 residents of the community in question meet the participant eligibility criteria.",
    "Recruitment method• The community/village is confirmed by the governmental committee of the town (after having been randomly selected), then preliminary screening of candidate participants will be conducted.",
    "Participants Inclusion criteria• Being 18 years old or above;• Having participated in two survey waves of the CMEC; • Having access to the internet via a smartphone.",
    "Exclusion criteria• Having a history of major psychiatric illnesses (e.g., schizophrenia and bipolar disorder), Parkinson's disease, severe cognitive or hearing impairment according to medical records obtained from Sichuan Medical Insurance Bureau."
  ],
